.TH PLSCOLBG 3plplot  "May, 2005" "" "PLplot API"
.SH NAME
\fBplscolbg\fP - Set the background color
by 8-bit RGB value 
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBplscolbg\fP(\fIr\fP, \fIg\fP, \fIb\fP)
.SH DESCRIPTION

.P
Set the background color (color 0 in color map 0) by 8-bit RGB value (see
the PLplot documentation). 
.SH ARGUMENTS
.TP
\fIr\fP (PLINT, input) 
Unsigned 8-bit integer (0-255) representing the degree of red in the color. 
.TP
\fIg\fP (PLINT, input) 
Unsigned 8-bit integer (0-255) representing the degree of green in the color. 
.TP
\fIb\fP (PLINT, input) 
Unsigned 8-bit integer (0-255) representing the degree of blue in the color. 

